{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783944241590,"sessionID":"ses_0a4a439a7ffeIer0f3SFvzBG1A","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_01_6O7wJMIzHjD3exKhCFoH2410","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/136-standalone-document-diff-skill/001-research-and-requirements/research/lineages/document-diff-3/deep-research-state.jsonl","content":"{\"type\":\"config\",\"topic\":\"Research the architecture and v1 contract for the standalone local AI document diff skill\",\"maxIterations\":10,\"convergenceThreshold\":0,\"stuckThreshold\":3,\"specFolder\":\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/136-standalone-document-diff-skill/001-research-and-requirements\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-07-13T15:00:00Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-document-diff-3-1783944168326-lgic9n\",\"stopPolicy\":\"max-iterations\"}\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/136-standalone-document-diff-skill/001-research-and-requirements/research/lineages/document-diff-3/deep-research-state.jsonl","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/136-standalone-document-diff-skill/001-research-and-requirements/research/lineages/document-diff-3/deep-research-state.jsonl","time":{"start":1783944241585,"end":1783944241589}},"id":"prt_f5b5cdac7001KJISlPU53Uyxs7","sessionID":"ses_0a4a439a7ffeIer0f3SFvzBG1A","messageID":"msg_f5b5ca9c0001dRznPzPLYYZYlE"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783944254674,"sessionID":"ses_0a4a439a7ffeIer0f3SFvzBG1A","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_02_TVMWl4UcOtW3kG4oN4Xd0811","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/136-standalone-document-diff-skill/001-research-and-requirements/research/lineages/document-diff-3/deep-research-strategy.md","content":"# Deep Research Strategy - Document Diff v1 Architecture\n\n## 2. TOPIC\nResearch the architecture and v1 contract for the standalone local AI document diff skill\n\n---\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:key-questions -->\n## 3. KEY QUESTIONS (remaining)\n- [ ] Q1: Which canonical representation and adapters should v1 use?\n- [ ] Q2: Which diff algorithms best suppress conversion noise?\n- [ ] Q3: Which snapshot lifecycle is safe and predictable?\n- [ ] Q4: How should the HTML report expose fidelity and risk?\n- [ ] Q5: Which portable core and skill interface should be implemented?\n- [ ] Q6: What format support matrix (text, Markdown, HTML, DOCX, PDF, scanned) is realistic for v1?\n- [ ] Q7: Which existing libraries/products provide authoritative evidence for these decisions?\n<!-- /ANCHOR:key-questions -->\n\n---\n\n## 4. NON-GOALS\n- Writing production parser, diff, snapshot, renderer, CLI, or skill code\n- Starting a hosted service, browser-only product, collaborative review system, or cloud sync\n- Persistent multi-version history beyond minimum baseline lifecycle\n- Claiming visual-layout equivalence from semantic extraction alone\n- Selecting implementation phases without citing converged research\n\n---\n\n## 5. STOP CONDITIONS\n- All 7 key questions have evidence-backed answers\n- 10 iterations completed (max-iterations policy)\n- No stop before max iterations (convergence threshold is 0)\n\n---\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:answered-questions -->\n## 6. ANSWERED QUESTIONS\n[None yet -- populated as iterations answer questions]\n<!-- /ANCHOR:answered-questions -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n<!-- ANCHOR:what-worked -->\n## 7. WHAT WORKED\n[First iteration -- populated after iteration 1 completes]\n<!-- /ANCHOR:what-worked -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:what-failed -->\n## 8. WHAT FAILED\n[First iteration -- populated after iteration 1 completes]\n<!-- /ANCHOR:what-failed -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:exhausted-approaches -->\n## 9. EXHAUSTED APPROACHES (do not retry)\n[Populated when an approach has been tried from multiple angles without success]\n<!-- /ANCHOR:exhausted-approaches -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:ruled-out-directions -->\n## 10. RULED OUT DIRECTIONS\n[Approaches that were investigated and definitively eliminated]\n<!-- /ANCHOR:ruled-out-directions -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:divergence-frontier -->\n## 10A. SATURATED DIRECTIONS AND DIVERGENCE FRONTIER\n- Completed pivots: 0\n- Failed pivots: 0\n- Saturated: none yet\n- Pivot lineage: none yet\n- Remaining frontier: none recorded\n<!-- /ANCHOR:divergence-frontier -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:carried-forward-open-questions -->\n## 11A. CARRIED-FORWARD OPEN QUESTIONS\n[none yet]\n<!-- /ANCHOR:carried-forward-open-questions -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:next-focus -->\n## 11. NEXT FOCUS\nQ1 + Q6: Survey canonical representations and format adapters — identify the v1 canonical document model\n<!-- /ANCHOR:next-focus -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n## 12. KNOWN CONTEXT\n\n### Bounded Context Snapshot\n\n- **Source pointers**: spec.md defines 6 P0 and 3 P1 requirements for v1 architecture research\n- **Resource map** is present at `resource-map.md` with 38 references across Commands, Skills, Specs, and Scripts\n- **Decision record ADR-001**: automatic local baseline snapshots, semantic/structural comparison, self-contained HTML, portable core + skill wrapper\n- **Theme summary**: Spec Kit owns packet structure, deep-research owns iterative evidence, sk-code/sk-doc supply authoring boundaries\n\n### Key constraints from spec:\n- Local-first: no Git, no network, no hosted account required\n- Format support tiers: full, limited, adapter-dependent, unsupported\n- HTML report must be self-contained, keyboard-navigable, XSS-safe\n- Portable core with stable interface, wrapped by one OpenCode skill\n\n---\n\n## 13. RESEARCH BOUNDARIES\n- Max iterations: 10\n- Convergence threshold: 0 (off — max-iterations policy)\n- Per-iteration budget: 12 tool calls, 10 minutes\n- Progressive synthesis: true\n- Current generation: 1\n- Started: 2026-07-13T15:00:00Z\n- Lineage: fanout-document-diff-3\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/136-standalone-document-diff-skill/001-research-and-requirements/research/lineages/document-diff-3/deep-research-strategy.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/136-standalone-document-diff-skill/001-research-and-requirements/research/lineages/document-diff-3/deep-research-strategy.md","time":{"start":1783944254662,"end":1783944254673}},"id":"prt_f5b5ce208001EicxGMSk9lRCbC","sessionID":"ses_0a4a439a7ffeIer0f3SFvzBG1A","messageID":"msg_f5b5ca9c0001dRznPzPLYYZYlE"}}
